<H3> <TI>   Leaders of Political Parties Review 1993 </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  OW0101023294 Ulaanbaatar MONTSAME in English 1308 GMT 31 Dec 
93 -- FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>

<F P=103> OW0101023294 </F>
