<H3> <TI>   Asian Development Bank To Help in New Projects </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  OW0601203594 Ulaanbaatar MONTSAME in English 1746 GMT 6 Jan 
94--FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>

<F P=103> OW0601203594 </F>
<F P=104>  Ulaanbaatar MONTSAME </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Ulaanbaatar, January 6 (OANA-MONTSAME) -- In the 
years from 1994-1997 with the participation of the Asian 
Development Bank there would be developed a number of new 
projects directed at solution of burning questions of the 
Mongolian economy. The major part of the credits and assistance 
of this weighty international organization will be used for a 
development of the agriculture and providing technological 
renovation for thermoelectric powers of Mongolia. In the new 
year for the purpose of providing the technical reconstruction 
of the thermoelectric power station the bank will grant to 
Mongolia some 35 million USD [U.S. dollars]. The Asian 
Development Bank will also finance the projects in the sphere of 
telecommunication, ecology construction of motorways and health 
protection of the population. 

