  [Text] Senator Mustapha Mohamed has been appointed Deputy 
Finance Minister to replace Datuk Abdul Ghani Othman, who is now 
the Youth and Sports Minister. 
  At the same time, Datuk Dr Ali Abu Sudin Omar has been 
